{"data":[{"date":"09:21 25/06","title":"\u0110\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Barca vs Real v\u00ec sao tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/barca-va-real-muon-mua-thiago-alcantara.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Barca v\u00e0 Real mu\u1ed1n mua Thiago Alcantara, hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Bayern Munich. M\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n y\u00eau c\u1ea7u n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 T\u00e2y Ban Nha ra \u0111i l\u00ean t\u1edbi 70 tri\u1ec7u Euro.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Barca mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Thiago</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nThiago Alcantara t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb Barcelona trong v\u00f2ng 6 n\u0103m (2005 t\u1edbi 2011). D\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Pep Guardiola, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00f4n l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i 1 v\u00e0 g\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou mu\u1ed1n anh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi k\u1ebf t\u1ee5c cho c\u00e1c c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n Xavi v\u00e0 Andres Iniesta.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Thiago kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edbi ng\u00e0y \u1ea5y. Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi hai bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00f3i tr\u00ean c\u1ee7a Barca, anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1ch ra \u0111i. \u0110\u1ea7u m\u00f9a 2013/14, Thiago \u0111i theo ti\u1ebfng g\u1ecdi c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y c\u0169 Guardiola t\u1ea1i Bayern Munich.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca v\u00e0 Real mu\u1ed1n mua Thiago Alcantara, hi\u1ec7n ch\u01a1i cho Bayern h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Barca v\u00e0 Real mu\u1ed1n mua Thiago Alcantara, hi\u1ec7n ch\u01a1i cho Bayern h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/barca-va-real-muon-mua-thiago-alcantara.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Barca mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 Thiago Alcantara</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng m\u00f9a 2014/15, qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian v\u1eeba qua ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Thiago h\u1ed3i sinh trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0110\u1ee9c. Qua \u0111\u00f3, anh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i gia bao g\u1ed3m ch\u00ednh CLB th\u1eddi ni\u00ean thi\u1ebfu Barcelona. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nG\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 x\u1ee9 Catalonia m\u1edbi chia tay Iniesta (sang Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n) v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf. Nh\u1eefng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd nh\u01b0 Andre Gomes hay Denis Suarez kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi HLV Ernesto Valverde.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>El Clasico v\u00ec tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 TBN</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng tin m\u00e0 t\u1edd Sport \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i, Barca v\u00e0 Real mu\u1ed1n mua Thiago Alcantara. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, Barca d\u00f9 mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c h\u1ed9i ng\u1ed9 v\u1edbi Thiago nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. Real c\u00f3 v\u0169 kh\u00ed l\u00e0 HLV Julen Lopetegui trong tay. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 51 tu\u1ed5i m\u1edbi nh\u1eadm ch\u1ee9c thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Los Blancos thay Zinedine Zidane n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay sau m\u00f9a 2017/18.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thiago Alcantara dinh chan thuong nghiem trong\" title=\"Thiago Alcantara d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/23/real-madrid-nham-nguoi-cu-barca-nang-cap-tuyen-giua.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Barca v\u00e0 Real mu\u1ed1n mua Thiago Alcantara</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Guardiola, Lopetegui l\u00e0 HLV c\u00f3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Thiago. H\u1ecd c\u00f9ng nhau g\u1eafn b\u00f3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i U19 t\u1edbi U21 T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh c\u00e1c ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t n\u0103m 2012 v\u00e0 2013. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Thiago, Real coi nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 tri\u1ec7t ti\u00eau s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Bayern Munich s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 Thiago ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 70 tri\u1ec7u Euro. M\u1ed9t con s\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 nh\u1ecf v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta ch\u1edd xem Real v\u00e0 Barca ai s\u1ebd b\u1ea1o tay h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/barca-real-va-psg-dai-chien-vi-sao-chelsea-172-189414.html\">Barca, Real v\u00e0 PSG \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec sao Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/sao-man-city-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-barca-180-189345.html\">Sao Man City c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-nham-sao-barca-nang-cap-hang-thu-172-189276.html\">MU nh\u1eafm sao Barca n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-muon-mua-sao-mu-sau-su-ra-di-cua-iniesta-180-189268.html\">Barca mu\u1ed1n mua sao M.U sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Iniesta</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"559","checkdouble":"189489"},{"date":"09:46 25/06","title":"M.U c\u1eed \u0111i\u1ec7p vi\u00ean th\u0103m d\u00f2 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i sao s\u00e1ng Serbia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/mu-muon-mua-milinkovicsavic-va-dung-chieu-doc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110ang b\u1eadn chinh chi\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i Nga c\u00f9ng \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia, nh\u01b0ng Hazard chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn tin m\u1eebng v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea7y m\u1edbi. Theo \u0111\u00f3, Chelsea b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Sarri trong th\u1eddi gian s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nConte \u0111i, Sarri \u0111\u1ebfn<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 gi\u00fap The Blues gi\u00e0nh 2 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch trong 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap FA g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, nh\u01b0ng HLV Antonio Conte v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ee9u chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Abramovich \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chia tay chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia t\u1eeb giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, nh\u01b0ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 b\u1ecb ng\u1eebng l\u1ea1i do nh\u1eefng r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i v\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 visa, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, Chelsea \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n th\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ea3o v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c sa th\u1ea3i Conte, khi h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u1ecf ra to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec1n b\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, c\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Juventus c\u01b0\u01a1ng quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ed9 khi c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i n\u00e0y chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, khi The Blues s\u1ebd c\u00f3 thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1edbi trong v\u00f2ng 24 gi\u1edd t\u1edbi &ndash; theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u1eeb b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh. HLV Maurizio Sarri s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea sau nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n t\u00edch c\u1ef1c. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n \u00f4ng c\u0169ng m\u1edbi b\u1ecb Napoli sa th\u1ea3i, v\u00e0 c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n t\u1ef1 do l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chia tay Conte, Chelsea b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Sarri thay th\u1ebf\" title=\"Antonio Conte Maurizio Sarri\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/30/Eden-Hazard-phat-bieu-ve-Chelsea-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chia tay Conte, Chelsea b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Sarri thay th\u1ebf</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edd Daily Star c\u00f2n cho bi\u1ebft th\u00eam, HLV Sarri y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ed1ng \u1edf khu Cobham, Surrey, g\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea1i b\u1ea3n doanh c\u1ee7a CLB. \u00d4ng s\u1ebd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 2 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Chelsea, c\u00f9ng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u00e9o d\u00e0i th\u00eam 1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u1eefa. 2 b\u00ean s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c k\u00fd k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng trong th\u1eddi gian s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, Sarri c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n m\u1eddi huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Chelsea &ndash; Gianfranco Zola gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng tin r\u1ea5t t\u00edch c\u1ef1c, v\u00ec The Blues \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch su\u00f4n s\u1ebb. Nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao nh\u01b0 Hazard hay Courtois c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u00f5 t\u00e2n HLV v\u00e0 tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u1edf l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed cho bi\u1ebft s\u1edf d\u0129 Chelsea b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Sarri, b\u1edfi h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch x\u1eed l\u00fd n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Antonio Conte. M\u00f9a h\u00e8 v\u1eeba qua, HLV n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111u\u1ed5i Diego Costa qua tin nh\u1eafn, khi\u1ebfn m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a anh b\u1ecb s\u1ee5t gi\u1ea3m th\u00ea th\u1ea3m (b\u00e1n cho Atletico v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 58 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-sarri-muon-chelsea-chi-70-trieu-bang-mua-thu-mon-nguoi-brazil-172-189429.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/11/hlv-sarri-muon-chelsea-chi-70-trieu-bang-mua-thu-mon-nguoi-brazil.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-sarri-muon-chelsea-chi-70-trieu-bang-mua-thu-mon-nguoi-brazil-172-189429.html\">HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n Chelsea chi 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil</span><br>\r\nMaurizio Sarri mu\u1ed1n Chelsea mua Alisson c\u1ee7a Roma, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 Thibaut Courtois ra \u0111i qua \u0111\u00f3 d\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00f3n th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-bo-nhiem-sarri-chuong-su-moi-voi-ga-nhan-vien-ngan-hang-172-187380.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/30/chelsea-bo-nhiem-sarri-thu-thach-long-kien-nhan-voi-ga-nhan-vien-ngan-hang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-bo-nhiem-sarri-chuong-su-moi-voi-ga-nhan-vien-ngan-hang-172-187380.html\">Chelsea b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Sarri: Ch\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1eed m\u1edbi v\u1edbi g\u00e3 nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng</span><br>\r\nChelsea b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Sarri thay th\u1ebf HLV Conte trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cao v\u00e0 qua \u0111\u00e2y, Stamford Bridge s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i, k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"558","checkdouble":"189490"},{"date":"09:05 25/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Saudi Arabia vs Ai C\u1eadp (21h00 ng\u00e0y 25/6): \u0110i t\u00ecm chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u1ecbch s\u1eed","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/nhan-dinh-saudi-arabia-vs-ai-cap-21h00-ngay-256-di-tim-chien-thang-lich-su.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ea3 Saudi Arabia l\u1eabn Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i World Cup n\u0103m nay. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n ng\u1ea9ng cao \u0111\u1ea7u r\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.</h2><h2>C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea3 Saudi Arabia l\u1eabn Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i sau khi lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai k\u1ebft th\u00fac. V\u00e0 tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00f4m nay ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh xem \u0111\u1ed9i n\u00e0o s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng l\u1ecbch s\u1eed.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSaudi Arabia hi\u1ec7n v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n n\u00e0o \u1edf World Cup. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua Uruguay \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai. V\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n gi\u1edd, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i World Cup k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u1ee7a Saeed Al-Owairan h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c B\u1ec9 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m 1994.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Saudi Arabia vs Ai C\u1eadp (21h00 ng\u00e0y 256) h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Saudi Arabia vs Ai C\u1eadp (21h00 ng\u00e0y 256) h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/Saudi-Arabia-vs-Ai-Cap.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Saudi Arabia vs Ai C\u1eadp</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nAi C\u1eadp th\u00ec th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf World Cup trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y. \u1ede l\u1ea7n tham d\u1ef1 s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1990, Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng sau nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng si\u00eau sao Mohamed Salah \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng B\u1eafc Phi. Salah v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n \u1edf <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> g\u1eb7p Uruguay v\u00e0 cho th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng anh ch\u01b0a b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga.</div>\r\n<h2>Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">X\u00e9t v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng quan l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Ai C\u1eadp l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u. \u0110o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Hector Cuper c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Ngo\u00e0i s\u1ef1 \u0111e d\u1ecda \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Mohamed Salah, Ai C\u1eadp c\u00f2n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trui r\u00e8n \u1edf Anh nh\u01b0 Elmohamady, Elneny hay Sobhi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Salah khong the giup Ai Cap danh bai Nga\" title=\"Salah kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nga\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/salah.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Salah kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, Saudi Arabia kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e0o thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, c\u1ea3 23 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n T\u00e2y \u00c1 \u0111\u1ec1u thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong n\u01b0\u1edbc. Vi\u1ec7c qu\u00e1 ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Al-Sahlawi c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn cho l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Saudi Arabia d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb b\u1eaft b\u00e0i v\u00e0 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y ch\u01b0a ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n n\u00e0o t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i, trong khi h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu 6 b\u00e0n thua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c si\u00eau sao Mohamed Salah \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u, Ai C\u1eadp s\u1ebd t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Salah \u0111ang l\u00e0 ngu\u1ed3n s\u1ed1ng ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a &ldquo;Pharaoh&rdquo; khi ghi t\u1edbi 5/7 b\u00e0n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. M\u1ed9t khi Salah l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t, anh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 h\u1ea1t nh\u00e2n gi\u00fap Ai C\u1eadp ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u1ee9ng chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn k\u00e9m c\u1ecfi trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u1ecbch s\u1eed t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i World Cup ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 Salah v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Saudi Arabia vs Ai C\u1eadp:</strong><br>\r\n- \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Saudi Arabia v\u00e0 Ai C\u1eadp t\u1ea1i World Cup. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, hai \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1eebng g\u1eb7p nhau \u1edf Confederations Cup n\u0103m 1999. \u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u \u00c1 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 5-1.<br>\r\n- Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cho Saudi Arabia ho\u1eb7c Ai C\u1eadp \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi s\u1ebd ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean thua c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng t\u1ea1i World Cup t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Honduras n\u0103m 2014.<br>\r\n- Saudi Arabia v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ghi b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 11 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf v\u00f2ng chung k\u1ebft World Cup. Honduras v\u00e0 Algeria n\u0103m 2010 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n- Saudi Arabia gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng trong 12 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf World Cup. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 thua 4 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n- \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u1edf World Cup.<br>\r\n- 8 b\u00e0n thua g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp t\u1ea1i World Cup \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn trong hi\u1ec7p hai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:</strong><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Saudi Arabia vs Ai Cap\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Saudi Arabia vs Ai C\u1eadp\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/Saudi-Arabia-vs-Ai-Cap-(4-2-3-1-vs-4-2-3-1).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Saudi Arabia vs Ai C\u1eadp</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1: 1-2</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Saudi Arabia vs Ai C\u1eadp:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/salah-len-tieng-sau-khi-ai-cap-som-bi-loai-khoi-world-cup-421-189235.html\">Salah l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng sau khi Ai C\u1eadp s\u1edbm b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/phu-thuoc-lionel-messi-argentina-co-hon-gi-ai-cap-466-189215.html\">Ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c Lionel Messi, Argentina c\u00f3 h\u01a1n g\u00ec... Ai C\u1eadp?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"557","checkdouble":"189491"},{"date":"10:29 25/06","title":"Kanu: \"Nigeria s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/bai-du-thi-an-tuong-world-cup-2018-brasil-vs-costa-rica.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Nwankwo Kanu tin r\u1eb1ng Nigeria c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 ti\u1ec1m l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D ng\u00e0y mai.</h2><h2>Nigeria c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Gernot Rohr \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafp b\u1eebng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland. V\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng thua trong tr\u1eadn t\u1eed chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Argentina t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Krestovsky ng\u00e0y mai, Nigeria s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00e2n v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/argentina-that-bai-khi-sampaoli-lac-me-hon-tran-421-189252.html\" target=\"_blank\">Argentina \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng</span>. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, La Albiceleste c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u201c\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng xanh\u201d n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kanu Nigeria s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kanu Nigeria s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/bai-du-thi-an-tuong-world-cup-2018-brasil-vs-costa-rica.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Kanu tin Nigeria s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Nwankwo Kanu tin r\u1eb1ng Nigeria th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ea1y cho Argentina m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cNigeria vs Argentina. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 tin kh\u00f4ng? Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i tin. V\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n kh\u00f4ng? T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3\u201d, Kanu chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean Twitter.</em><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u k\u00e9m</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Rohr \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Argentina v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 4-2 trong tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu t\u1ea1i Krasnodar. Nh\u01b0ng trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, Argentina v\u1eabn lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 k\u1ef5 gi\u01a1 c\u1ee7a Nigeria.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u Phi ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd th\u1eafng La Albiceleste trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed FIFA World Cup. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua trong t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nArgentina \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i s\u1edbm sau hai tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland v\u00e0 Croatia. K\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 c\u00f3 th\u1eafng Nigeria, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Nam M\u1ef9 c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Iceland th\u1eafng Croatia \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, Argentina s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ee7 l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Iceland tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng. C\u00f2n n\u1ebfu Iceland kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Croatia, Argentina ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n th\u1eafng v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Argentina:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/messi-chi-chia-tay-dt-argentina-voi-mot-dieu-kien-421-189475.html\">Messi ch\u1ec9 chia tay \u0110T Argentina v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/noi-bo-tuyen-argentina-dang-roi-nhu-canh-he-421-189422.html\">N\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec3n Argentina \u0111ang r\u1ed1i nh\u01b0 canh h\u1eb9</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"556","checkdouble":"189492"},{"date":"10:47 25/06","title":"Hazard chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00f3 th\u1ea7y m\u1edbi trong 24 gi\u1edd t\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/19/hazard-chuan-bi-co-thay-moi-trong-24-gio-toi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110ang b\u1eadn chinh chi\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i Nga c\u00f9ng \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia, nh\u01b0ng Hazard chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn tin m\u1eebng v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea7y m\u1edbi. Theo \u0111\u00f3, Chelsea b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Sarri trong th\u1eddi gian s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nConte \u0111i, Sarri \u0111\u1ebfn<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 gi\u00fap The Blues gi\u00e0nh 2 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch trong 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap FA g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, nh\u01b0ng HLV Antonio Conte v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ee9u chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Abramovich \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chia tay chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia t\u1eeb giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, nh\u01b0ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 b\u1ecb ng\u1eebng l\u1ea1i do nh\u1eefng r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i v\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 visa, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, Chelsea \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n th\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ea3o v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c sa th\u1ea3i Conte, khi h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u1ecf ra to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec1n b\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, c\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Juventus c\u01b0\u01a1ng quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ed9 khi c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i n\u00e0y chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, khi The Blues s\u1ebd c\u00f3 thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1edbi trong v\u00f2ng 24 gi\u1edd t\u1edbi &ndash; theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u1eeb b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh. HLV Maurizio Sarri s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea sau nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n t\u00edch c\u1ef1c. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n \u00f4ng c\u0169ng m\u1edbi b\u1ecb Napoli sa th\u1ea3i, v\u00e0 c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n t\u1ef1 do l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chia tay Conte, Chelsea b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Sarri thay th\u1ebf\" title=\"Antonio Conte Maurizio Sarri\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/30/Eden-Hazard-phat-bieu-ve-Chelsea-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chia tay Conte, Chelsea b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Sarri thay th\u1ebf</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edd Daily Star c\u00f2n cho bi\u1ebft th\u00eam, HLV Sarri y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ed1ng \u1edf khu Cobham, Surrey, g\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea1i b\u1ea3n doanh c\u1ee7a CLB. \u00d4ng s\u1ebd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 2 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Chelsea, c\u00f9ng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u00e9o d\u00e0i th\u00eam 1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u1eefa. 2 b\u00ean s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c k\u00fd k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng trong th\u1eddi gian s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, Sarri c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n m\u1eddi huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Chelsea &ndash; Gianfranco Zola gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng tin r\u1ea5t t\u00edch c\u1ef1c, v\u00ec The Blues \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch su\u00f4n s\u1ebb. Nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao nh\u01b0 Hazard hay Courtois c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u00f5 t\u00e2n HLV v\u00e0 tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u1edf l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed cho bi\u1ebft s\u1edf d\u0129 Chelsea b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Sarri, b\u1edfi h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch x\u1eed l\u00fd n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Antonio Conte. M\u00f9a h\u00e8 v\u1eeba qua, HLV n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111u\u1ed5i Diego Costa qua tin nh\u1eafn, khi\u1ebfn m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a anh b\u1ecb s\u1ee5t gi\u1ea3m th\u00ea th\u1ea3m (b\u00e1n cho Atletico v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 58 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-sarri-muon-chelsea-chi-70-trieu-bang-mua-thu-mon-nguoi-brazil-172-189429.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/11/hlv-sarri-muon-chelsea-chi-70-trieu-bang-mua-thu-mon-nguoi-brazil.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-sarri-muon-chelsea-chi-70-trieu-bang-mua-thu-mon-nguoi-brazil-172-189429.html\">HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n Chelsea chi 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil</span><br>\r\nMaurizio Sarri mu\u1ed1n Chelsea mua Alisson c\u1ee7a Roma, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 Thibaut Courtois ra \u0111i qua \u0111\u00f3 d\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00f3n th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-bo-nhiem-sarri-chuong-su-moi-voi-ga-nhan-vien-ngan-hang-172-187380.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/30/chelsea-bo-nhiem-sarri-thu-thach-long-kien-nhan-voi-ga-nhan-vien-ngan-hang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-bo-nhiem-sarri-chuong-su-moi-voi-ga-nhan-vien-ngan-hang-172-187380.html\">Chelsea b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Sarri: Ch\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1eed m\u1edbi v\u1edbi g\u00e3 nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng</span><br>\r\nChelsea b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Sarri thay th\u1ebf HLV Conte trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cao v\u00e0 qua \u0111\u00e2y, Stamford Bridge s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i, k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"555","checkdouble":"189498"},{"date":"10:19 25/06","title":"Quy t\u1eafc x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i trong b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/quy-tac-xep-hang-bang-dau-world-cup-2018-tai-sao-anh-vs-bi-co-the-phan-dinh-nhat-nhi-bang-the-phat.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua hai l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0 t\u1eeb t\u1ed1i nay, World Cup 2018 s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t 16 t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p hai hay nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1, quy t\u1eafc x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ra sao?</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u01a1n c\u1eed r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh c\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u1edf b\u1ea3ng G, khi c\u1ea3 Anh v\u00e0 B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia v\u00e0 Panama \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edbm gi\u00e0nh hai v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t cu\u1ed1i s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec ng\u00f4i v\u1ecb s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t h\u00f2ng t\u1ea1o l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n knock-out.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chi ti\u1ebft quy t\u1eafc x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chi ti\u1ebft quy t\u1eafc x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/Chi-tiet-quy-tac-xep-hang-bang-dau-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.png\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>X\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng b\u1ea3ng G sau hai l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn World Cup 2018: Anh vs B\u1ec9 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u00fa v\u1ecb l\u00e0 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y: Anh v\u00e0 B\u1ec9 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1edf h\u1eefu 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m, hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 +6 v\u00e0 ghi 8 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. V\u1edbi t\u01b0\u01a1ng quan l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a nhau l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i cao v\u00e0 khi \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ecdi ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n c\u0169ng s\u1ebd c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng. Ban t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c World Cup s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m sao \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec?<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p hy h\u1eefu n\u00e0y, <em><strong>ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 fair-play</strong></em> s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e9t t\u1edbi, c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 xoay quanh ch\u00ednh nh\u1eefng t\u1ea5m th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t m\u00e0 n\u00f3i n\u00f4m na, ai nh\u1eadn nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n th\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00f3 thi\u1ec7t v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 c\u00e1ch t\u00ednh \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0 sau: m\u1ed7i th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng s\u1ebd b\u1ecb tr\u1eeb 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m, th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf gi\u00e1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1eeb hai th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng s\u1ebd b\u1ecb tr\u1eeb 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp s\u1ebd b\u1ecb tr\u1eeb 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m, v\u00e0 th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp sau khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd b\u1ecb tr\u1eeb \u0111\u1ebfn 5 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">L\u1ee3i th\u1ebf hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0111ang thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh khi h\u1ecd m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 nh\u1eadn hai th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng so v\u1edbi ba c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9. Tuy nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec3m b\u1ecb tr\u1eeb do th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t, FIFA s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh b\u1ed1c th\u0103m may r\u1ee7i \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00f4i th\u1ee9.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><em>Nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00e2y, Bongda24h.vn c\u0169ng xin cung c\u1ea5p cho qu\u00fd \u0111\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 th\u1ee9 t\u1ef1 c\u00e1c ti\u00eau ch\u00ed s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp \u01b0u ti\u00ean cho c\u00e1ch t\u00ednh th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c lu\u1eadt FIFA gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 \u1edf \u0111i\u1ec1u 32.5 trang 43 -&nbsp;</em></strong><b><i>Quy t\u1eafc x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u World Cup 2018:</i></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><em>* \u00c1p d\u1ee5ng cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, th\u1ee9 t\u1ef1 x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i trong m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean c\u00e1c y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1:</em> <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">1. S\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c; <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">2. Hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng b\u1ea1i; <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">3. S\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><em>* Ngo\u00e0i ra, trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t hai \u0111\u1ed9i ngang b\u1eb1ng nhau trong t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c ti\u00eau ch\u00ed tr\u00ean, th\u1ee9 t\u1ef1 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u01b0 sau:</em><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">4. Gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5t trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e9t c\u00f9ng \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. (C\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f9ng hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 c\u00f9ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng);<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">5. Hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng thua t\u00ednh trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e9t c\u00f9ng \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">6. Ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e9t c\u00f9ng \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">7. \u0110i\u1ec3m fairplay cao nh\u1ea5t d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean s\u1ed1 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng v\u00e0 th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">- Th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng: -1 \u0111i\u1ec3m;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">- Th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf gi\u00e1n ti\u1ebfp (2 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng): -3 \u0111i\u1ec3m;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">- Th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp: -4 \u0111i\u1ec3m;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">- Th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng + th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp: -5 \u0111i\u1ec3m (M\u1ed7i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ec9 b\u1ecb tr\u1eeb 1 l\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi 1 trong c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean, trong 1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">8. B\u1ed1c th\u0103m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i ngo\u00e0i b\u1ea3ng G c\u1ee7a Anh v\u00e0 B\u1ec9, nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3ng A c\u1ee7a Nga v\u00e0 Uruguay, b\u1ea3ng B c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha hay \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p hai b\u1ea3ng F (\u0110\u1ee9c, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, Mexico, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c) v\u00e0 b\u1ea3ng H (Colombia, Senegal, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n) \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cao ph\u1ea3i ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c ti\u00eau ch\u00ed ph\u1ee5 ngo\u00e0i \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 t\u1ed5ng quan.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Quy tac xep hang bang dau World Cup 2018: Anh vs Bi phan dinh nhat nhi bang the phat?\" title=\"Quy t\u1eafc x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u World Cup 2018: Anh vs B\u1ec9 ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec b\u1eb1ng th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t?\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/5.png\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Quy t\u1eafc x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u World Cup 2018: Anh vs B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec b\u1eb1ng s\u1ed1 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t?</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br />\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/cuc-dien-bang-f-truoc-vong-dau-cuoi-tu-than-goi-ten-ai-421-189382.html\">C\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n b\u1ea3ng F tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i: T\u1eed th\u1ea7n g\u1ecdi t\u00ean ai?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/cuc-dien-bang-h-truoc-luot-tran-cuoi-cho-doi-nhung-bat-ngo-421-189462.html\">C\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n b\u1ea3ng H tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i: \u0110i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thua-tham-croatia-argentina-phai-lam-gi-de-vuot-qua-vong-bang-421-189208.html\">Thua th\u1ea3m Croatia, Argentina ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"554","checkdouble":"189499"},{"date":"11:10 25/06","title":"Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n h\u1ee3p t\u00ecnh cho tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u s\u1edbm Nga vs Uruguay","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/nhan-dinh-nga-vs-uruguay-va-du-doan-soi-keo-uruguay-vs-nga.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nga vs Uruguay thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 sau nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. V\u1eabn b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n Uruguay song \u201cNh\u1eefng ch\u00fa g\u1ea5u\u201d c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t.</h2><br>\r\n<h2>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn</h2>\r\n- <strong>Nga t\u1eeb h\u00f2a t\u1edbi th\u1eafng</strong><br>\r\n- <strong>\u00cdt b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</strong> (t\u1eeb 2 tr\u1edf xu\u1ed1ng)<br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: <strong>H\u00f2a 0-0<br>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<h2>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u: </em>Nga vs Uruguay<br>\r\n<em>Th\u1eddi gian:</em> 21h ng\u00e0y 25/6<br>\r\n<em>\u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m: </em>S\u00e2n Samara Arena<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>TLCA c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn: </em>Nga 1.00*0:0*0.94 Uruguay<br>\r\n<em>TBT c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn: </em>Nhi\u1ec1u 0.85*2*-0.93 \u00cdt<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nga vs Uruguay v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u00e0ng tr\u00ean Bongda24h h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nga vs Uruguay v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u00e0ng tr\u00ean Bongda24h h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/nhan-dinh-nga-vs-uruguay-va-du-doan-soi-keo-uruguay-vs-nga.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nga vs Uruguay 21h ng\u00e0y 25/6</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>Nga kh\u00f4ng thua</h2>\r\n<br>\r\nNga \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out World Cup 2018 sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng 3-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ai C\u1eadp v\u00e0 Uruguay \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Saudi Arabia 1-0. \u0110o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Stanislav Cherchesov \u0111ang c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng A m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c v\u1edbi 8 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 1 l\u1ea7n l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ecf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1eb1ng sau chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 \u00fd, Nga \u0111\u00e3 \u201cl\u1ed9t x\u00e1c\u201d khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o World Cup 2018. D\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng l\u1ea1i v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh gi\u00fap HLV Cherchesov t\u00ecm ra \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi tuyen Nga\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Nga\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/3-yeu-to-giup-nga-da-bai-ai-cap-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nga to\u00e0n th\u1eafng 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng su\u1ed1t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Nga bay cao. Nh\u1eefng Aleksandr Golovin, Denis Cheryshev r\u1ed3i Artem Dzyuba\u2026 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 b\u1ea1ch d\u01b0\u01a1ng. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd mang kh\u00ed th\u1ebf \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u tranh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Uruguay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nga vs Uruguay c\u0169ng nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0. 2 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua, Nga \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u. 8 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 2 tr\u1eadn l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 cho th\u1ea5y c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111a d\u1ea1ng cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Cherchesov.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nguoi-hung-dt-nga-muon-cham-tran-doi-thu-nao-o-vong-knockout-421-189236.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/nguoi-hung-dt-nga-muon-cham-tran-doi-thu-nao-o-vong-knockout.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nguoi-hung-dt-nga-muon-cham-tran-doi-thu-nao-o-vong-knockout-421-189236.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng \u0110T Nga mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o \u1edf v\u00f2ng knock-out?</span><br>\r\n<span>Ghi 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn c\u00f9ng \u0110T Nga l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u1edf m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup, ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i Denis Cheryshev \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra t\u1ef1 tin n\u1ebfu g\u1eb7p...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNga c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u00e1p \u0111\u1eb7t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Saudi Arabia 5-0. Tuy nhi\u00ean, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00f9i l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t hay tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uruguay. S\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1ee7a Nga l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u00ednh to\u00e1n \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u01a1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ai ngh\u0129 c\u1eb7p ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m Roman Zobnin v\u00e0 Yury Gazinskiy l\u1ea1i ch\u01a1i hay \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1eady khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o World Cup 2018. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00e0y \u1ea3i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ecdc t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Sergei Ignashevich.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nUruguay v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t trong t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng (s\u1ebd ph\u00e2n t\u00edch d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y) v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng m\u1ea1ch b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Nga s\u1ebd ch\u01b0a d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Ch\u1ecdn: </strong>Nga t\u1eeb h\u00f2a t\u1edbi th\u1eafng<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>\u00cdt b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</h2>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Uruguay sau 2 tr\u1eadn khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y\u2026 nh\u00e0n nh\u1ea1t. S\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ki\u1ec3m ch\u1ee9ng. V\u1edbi 3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u00f9ng nhau nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110TQG v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t gi\u00e0u t\u00ednh chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0 Jose Gimenez, Diego Godin v\u00e0 Martin Caceres, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ea7y v\u1eefng v\u00e0ng trong su\u1ed1t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n2 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ai C\u1eadp v\u00e0 Saudi Arabia n\u00e2ng chu\u1ed7i gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Uruguay l\u00ean con s\u1ed1 5. <br>\r\nM\u1edf r\u1ed9ng h\u01a1n, 11 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua c\u1ea3 giao h\u1eefu v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c, La Celeste ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ecbu c\u00f3 5 b\u00e0n thua. Ngo\u00e0i c\u00e1c nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, tri\u1ebft l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Uruguay c\u0169ng l\u00e0 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf t\u1ed1i \u0111a c\u00e1c b\u00e0n thua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ai Cap 0-1 Uruguay\" title=\"Ai C\u1eadp 0-1 Uruguay\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/uruguay-ra-quan-that-vong-khon-khong-den-tre.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Uruguay th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn sau 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 qua</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i v\u1edbi Saudi Arabia ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n. Ngay sau khi c\u00f3 b\u00e0n d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, HLV Oscar Tabarez l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c xua qu\u00e2n v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 khung th\u00e0nh v\u00e0 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng. C\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 tri\u1ec3n khai t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n tuy\u1ebfn Uruguay \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc Ai C\u1eadp, m\u00ecnh Luis Suarez \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 3 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ngon \u0103n. Khi \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Barcelona ho\u1eb7c d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m thi\u1ebfu ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c, ho\u1eb7c t\u1ecf ra thi\u1ebfu nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc Saudi Arabia, khi Uruguay ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn th\u1eddi gian ch\u01a1i ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng, s\u1ef1 ch\u1eadm ch\u1ea1p c\u1ee7a Suarez kh\u00f4ng gi\u00fap \u00edch nhi\u1ec1u cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Luis Suarez bo lo co hoi\" title=\"Luis Suarez bo lo co hoi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/Luis-Suarez-bo-lo-co-hoi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u01b0ng h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Uruguay \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Suarez \u0111\u00e3 phung ph\u00ed c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nRi\u00eang v\u1edbi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nga vs Uruguay, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn HLV Tabarez ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 t\u00ednh to\u00e1n. C\u1ea3 Suarez v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c Cavani \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc qua tu\u1ed5i 31 v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e3 suy gi\u1ea3m. N\u1ebfu b\u1eaft h\u1ecd d\u1ed1c s\u1ee9c v\u00ec cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nga, e r\u1eb1ng s\u1ebd qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n2 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 Nga v\u00e0 Uruguay c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1eb7p \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 l\u00e0 T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha th\u1ef1c ra kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch nhau v\u1ec1 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh. Xem ra \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n bung s\u1ee9c l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1 v\u1edbi Nga \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i th\u1ea5t th\u1ebf trong vi\u1ec7c \u0111i \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00e0i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi Nga, h\u1ecd th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng do v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i v\u1ec1 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u2013 b\u1ea1i (+7 so v\u1edbi +2). S\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7m ch\u1eebng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea9y tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi \u0111i v\u00e0o vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh khan hi\u1ebfm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Ch\u1ecdn:</strong> \u00cdt b\u00e0n th\u1eafng<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn</h2>\r\n- <strong>Nga t\u1eeb h\u00f2a t\u1edbi th\u1eafng</strong><br>\r\n- <strong>\u00cdt b\u00e0n th\u1eafng </strong>(t\u1eeb 2 tr\u1edf xu\u1ed1ng)<br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: <strong>H\u00f2a 0-0<br>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<h2>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t kh\u00e1c:</h2>\r\n- S\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ee7a Nga c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u00edt h\u01a1n (+1/4)<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ee7a Nga c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u00edt h\u01a1n (+0)<br>\r\n- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 10 (O 9 1/2)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ea3i Ly (TTVN)<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"553","checkdouble":"189505"},{"date":"11:13 25/06","title":"Hy h\u1eefu: M\u1ed9t C\u0110V Anh l\u1eb7n l\u1ed9i ng\u00e0n d\u1eb7m t\u1edbi Nga v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n\u2026 qu\u00ean v\u00e9 \u1edf nh\u00e0","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/hy-huu-mot-cdv-anh-lan-loi-ngan-dam-toi-nga-va-phat-hien-quen-ve-o-nha.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 \u0111\u00e1ng bu\u1ed3n (c\u01b0\u1eddi) \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra, khi m\u1ed9t C\u0110V Anh qu\u00ean v\u00e9 xem World Cup \u1edf nh\u00e0, d\u00f9 t\u1ed1n v\u00f4 v\u00e0n c\u00f4ng s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1edbi ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh.\r\n</h2><h2><br />\r\nS\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 hy h\u1eefu c\u1ee7a fan \u0110T Anh<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua, Tam S\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, khi h\u1ecd h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Panama v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t set tennis. H\u00f2a chung ni\u1ec1m vui v\u1edbi c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn nh\u1eefng C\u0110V may m\u1eafn g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i Nga th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac h\u01a1n ai h\u1ebft.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u1ebd ra l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean Douglas Moreton, nh\u01b0ng th\u1eadt ti\u1ebfc, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, C\u0110V n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 di chuy\u1ec3n m\u1ed9t qu\u00e3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng 3200 d\u1eb7m (h\u01a1n 5000 km) \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i Nizhny Novgorod, mi\u1ec1n T\u00e2y n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga, \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m di\u1ec5n ra tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa tuy\u1ec3n Anh vs Panama. Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i, \u00f4ng ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh b\u1ecf qu\u00ean chi\u1ebfc v\u00e9 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n trong m\u1ed9t ng\u0103n k\u00e9o \u1edf nh\u00e0.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngay khi ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n ra sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eddi, \u00f4ng Douglas Moreton \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ecfi xem ai \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfc v\u00e9 cho m\u00ecnh. May thay, C\u0110V n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf c\u00f9ng kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n v\u1edbi bi\u00ean t\u1eadp vi\u00ean Dan Howells c\u1ee7a ITV News, v\u00e0 l\u1eddi k\u00eau g\u1ecdi n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i tr\u00ean Twitter.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ng\u00e0n d\u1eb7m t\u1edbi Nga, m\u1ed9t C\u0110V Anh qu\u00ean v\u00e9 xem World Cup \u1edf nh\u00e0 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ng\u00e0n d\u1eb7m t\u1edbi Nga, m\u1ed9t C\u0110V Anh qu\u00ean v\u00e9 xem World Cup \u1edf nh\u00e0 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/Ngan-dam-toi-Nga,-mot-CDV-Anh-quen-ve-xem-World-Cup-o-nha-hinh-anh.png\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bi\u00ean t\u1eadp vi\u00ean Dan Howells c\u00f9ng Douglas Moreton, C\u0110V Anh qu\u00ean v\u00e9 xem World Cup \u1edf nh\u00e0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<em>&ldquo;Xin ch\u00e0o, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 Douglas, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf Volgograd \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ed5 v\u0169 \u0110T Anh, nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i b\u1ecf qu\u00ean chi\u1ebfc v\u00e9 \u1edf nh\u00e0 t\u1ea1i Bristol. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Tam S\u01b0 v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 ng\u00e0n d\u1eb7m xa x\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai c\u00f2n th\u1eeba v\u00e9, h\u00e3y cho t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft&rdquo;</em> &ndash; l\u1eddi k\u00eau g\u1ecdi c\u1ee7a bi\u00ean t\u1eadp vi\u00ean Dan Howells.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 khi d\u00f2ng tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi li\u00ean l\u1ea1c v\u1edbi Howells v\u00e0 nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc v\u00e9. Tuy nhi\u00ean, s\u1ed1 ph\u1eadn v\u1eabn tr\u00eau ng\u01b0\u01a1i C\u0110V Douglas Moreton khi \u00f4ng&hellip; \u0111i v\u1eafng kh\u1ecfi kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n \u0111\u00fang th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eadt \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc v\u1edbi C\u0110V Anh qu\u00ean v\u00e9 xem World Cup, b\u1edfi \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf qua <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-anh-vs-panama-463-189421.html\" target=\"_blank\">chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Panama.</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-anh-vs-panama-461-189431.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/clip-ban-thang-anh-vs-panama.JPG\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-anh-vs-panama-461-189431.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Anh 6-1 Panama (B\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018)</span><br />\r\nV\u1eabn bi\u1ebft Panama kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 x\u1ee9ng t\u1ea7m v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Southgate song t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean khi Tam s\u01b0 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t. Trong \u0111\u00f3, trung v\u1ec7...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/anh-ha-guc-tunisia-mot-cdv-nhay-len-nap-capo-an-mung-421-188942.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/anh-ha-guc-tunisia-mot-cdv-nhay-len-nap-capo-an-mung.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/anh-ha-guc-tunisia-mot-cdv-nhay-len-nap-capo-an-mung-421-188942.html\">Anh h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Tunisia, m\u1ed9t C\u0110V&hellip; nh\u1ea3y l\u00ean n\u1eafp capo \u0103n m\u1eebng</span><br />\r\nSong song v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c si\u00eau sao t\u1ea1i VCK World Cup 2018, c\u00e1c kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 tr\u00ean kh\u1eafp th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u0169ng lu\u00f4n bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch \u0103n m\u1eebng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, m\u1ed9t C\u0110V...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nNguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"552","checkdouble":"189506"},{"date":"11:31 25/06","title":"Luke Shaw khi\u1ebfn Mourinho ph\u00e1t ch\u00e1n khi l\u1ed9 \u201cb\u1ee5ng b\u1ea7u\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/21/luke-shaw-khien-mourinho-phat-chan-khi-lo-bung-bau.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u00e1c C\u0110V Man United \u0111ang ng\u00e1n ng\u1ea9m khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Luke Shaw ph\u00e1t t\u01b0\u1edbng trong k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8.\r\n</h2><h2>Shaw l\u00ean c\u00e2n ch\u00f3ng m\u1eb7t<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110ang \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai kh\u00f4ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u1edf Old Trafford, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Luke Shaw ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh l\u1ea1i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, anh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e0y \u1ea3i tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb v\u00ec nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp kh\u00f4ng chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u1eabn quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh trao cho Luke Shaw th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, khi nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111em v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, c\u00f3 th\u00f4ng tin Luke Shaw \u0111ang r\u00e2t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u00e8n luy\u1ec7n trong th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i, l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1ea7m. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh &ldquo;ch\u1ed9p&rdquo; \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y \u0111ang \u0103n ch\u01a1i &ldquo;ph\u00e8 ph\u1ee1n&rdquo; t\u1ea1i b\u00e3i bi\u1ec3n n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng Ibiza, n\u01a1i v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn trong m\u1ed7i k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, Luke Shaw ph\u00e1t t\u01b0\u1edbng v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c C\u0110V kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn ra h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"S\u1ed1c v\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh Luke Shaw ph\u00e1t t\u01b0\u1edbng trong k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8\" title=\"S\u1ed1c v\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh Luke Shaw ph\u00e1t t\u01b0\u1edbng trong k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/Soc-voi-hinh-anh-Luke-Shaw-phat-tuong-trong-ky-nghi-he-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Luke Shaw ph\u00e1t t\u01b0\u1edbng trong k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nV\u1edbi th\u00e2n h\u00ecnh &ldquo;c\u1ed3ng k\u1ec1nh&rdquo; nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i Man United, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a anh \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u khi Jose Mourinho v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Asley Young &ndash; m\u1ed9t &ldquo;\u00f4ng gi\u00e0&rdquo; 32 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh, khi th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2014, nh\u01b0ng Luke Shaw ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi y\u00eau qu\u00fd m\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. T\u1eebng l\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i tri\u1ec3n v\u1ecdng s\u1ed1 1 x\u1ee9 s\u1edf s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9, gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y Shaw ph\u1ea3i theo d\u00f5i \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1 World Cup, trong t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng v\u00e1c &ldquo;b\u1ee5ng b\u1ea7u&rdquo;.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi c\u00f2n 2 th\u00e1ng n\u1eefa s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra, v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh Luke Shaw ph\u00e1t t\u01b0\u1edbng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n, g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec3 anh \u1edf l\u1ea1i Old Trafford.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-bi-chi-trich-vi-cach-doi-xu-voi-3-cau-thu-mu-172-186875.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/20/mourinho-bi-chi-trich-vi-cach-doi-xu-voi-3-cau-thu-mu.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-bi-chi-trich-vi-cach-doi-xu-voi-3-cau-thu-mu-172-186875.html\">Mourinho b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00ec c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed v\u1edbi 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 MU</span><br />\r\nHuy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Ian Wright l\u00ean \u00e1n HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha sau nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0 \u0111ang l\u00e0m v\u1edbi Marcus Rashford, Paul Pogba v\u00e0 Luke Shaw.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-nhin-mu-chieu-mo-diogo-dalot-172-187924.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/7/goc-nhin-mu-chieu-mo-diogo-dalot.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-nhin-mu-chieu-mo-diogo-dalot-172-187924.html\">G\u00f3c M.U: 17 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Diogo Dalot l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00f3n h\u1eddi!</span><br />\r\nT\u1ed1i qua (6/6), th\u00f4ng tin ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1: MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Diogo Dalot t\u1eeb Porto. Nh\u01b0 l\u1eddi HLV Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh hay nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"551","checkdouble":"189507"},{"date":"08:04 25/06","title":"C\u0110V th\u00edch th\u00fa v\u1edbi m\u00e0n b\u1eaby vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Senegal c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/cdv-thich-thu-voi-man-bay-viet-vi-nua-doi-hinh-senegal-cua-nguoi-nhat.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tinh th\u1ea7n \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c theo nh\u00f3m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t huy t\u1ed1i \u0111a trong pha Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n b\u1eaby vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb khi\u1ebfn 6 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Senegal b\u1ecb tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i th\u1ed5i ph\u1ea1t. </h2><div style=\"text - align:center; width: 100 %; padding: 20px 0; \"><video data-dashjs-player=\"\" src=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/DRM/201806/273445/stream.mpd\" controls=\"\"></video></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u0110V th\u00edch th\u00fa v\u1edbi m\u00e0n Nh\u1eadt b\u1eaby vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Senegal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u0110V th\u00edch th\u00fa v\u1edbi m\u00e0n Nh\u1eadt b\u1eaby vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Senegal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/0_1.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111ang g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 nh\u1edd m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 c\u00f9ng tinh th\u1ea7n qu\u1eadt c\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng run s\u1ee3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh. Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Senegal, c\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn binh Samurai khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 th\u00e1n ph\u1ee5c v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t pha b\u1eaby vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Sadio Mane th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00fa s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t, to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t d\u00e2ng cao b\u1ecf l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t m\u00e0 l\u00e0 6 c\u00e1i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o tr\u1eafng ng\u1ea9n ng\u01a1 khi b\u1ecb tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i bi\u00ean c\u0103ng c\u1edd b\u00e1o vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"1\" title=\"1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/1_2.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\"B\u1eaby vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi\", t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n So Mexican th\u00e1n ph\u1ee5c.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"1\" title=\"1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/2_2.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\"T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng b\u1eaby vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi nh\u1ea5t t\u00f4i t\u1eebng ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn. 6 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Senegal \u0111\u00e3 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o th\u1ebf vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb. Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng l\u00e0 b\u1eadc th\u1ea7y\".</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"1\" title=\"1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/3_3.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\"K\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt v\u00e0 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft. M\u1ed9t pha b\u1eaby vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o\".</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"1\" title=\"1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/4_1.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\"\u0110\u00f3 c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 pha b\u1eaby vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed World Cup kh\u00f4ng? Ch\u00fac m\u1eebng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n\", nickname 3wuor t\u1ef1 h\u1ecfi.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"1\" title=\"1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/5_1.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\"Nh\u1eadt \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng b\u1eaby vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb th\u1ed5i ph\u1ea1t\".</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"1\" title=\"1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/080333-6.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\"Ch\u00faa \u01a1i, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1eaby vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t xa gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a lo\u00e0i ng\u01b0\u1eddi\", m\u1ed9t C\u0110V th\u00e1n ph\u1ee5c. </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br /></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"550","checkdouble":"189477"},{"date":"08:18 25/06","title":"S\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 hy h\u1eefu: Sao tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ecb thay ra v\u00ec\u2026 h\u1ebft \u00e1o m\u1eb7c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/su-co-hy-huu-sao-tuyen-duc-bi-thay-ra-vi-het-ao-mac.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c, Sebastian Rudy \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n gi\u1eefa hi\u1ec7p 1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u00ec l\u00fd do kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee1.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00eam qua, Sebastian Rudy \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Joachim Low ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00e1 thay v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Sami Khedira. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t cho \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00fat 25, th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m anh d\u00ednh nguy\u00ean c\u00fa \u0111\u1ea1p h\u1eadu c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u00e0o m\u1eb7t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00fa \u0111\u1ea1p v\u00f4 \u00fd c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n khi\u1ebfn Sebastian Rudy ch\u1ea3y m\u00e1u r\u00f2ng r\u00f2ng v\u00e0 c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c b\u00e1c s\u0129. Tuy nhi\u00ean, sau khi v\u1ebft th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1eed l\u00fd, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 \u0110\u1ee9c n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n v\u00ec l\u00fd do tr\u1eddi \u01a1i.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/180624_141340_109.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng \u0110\u1ee9c, Sebastian Rudy ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i ti\u1ebfp nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n. Theo lu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a FIFA, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i thay \u00e1o d\u00ednh m\u00e1u \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c v\u00e0o s\u00e2n. BHL \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 HLV Joachim Low c\u0169ng ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn ch\u1edd Sebastian Rudy kho\u1ea3ng 5 ph\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng 10 \u0111\u1ea5u 11 qu\u00e1 l\u00e2u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch t\u1ea1i sao Sebastian Rudy l\u1ea1i c\u1edfi tr\u1ea7n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee9ng r\u1ea5t l\u00e2u \u1edf khu v\u1ef1c k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c. Kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u khi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich sau \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn ra m\u1eb7t v\u00e0 n\u00e9m h\u1ebft \u00e1o \u0111i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV \u0110\u1ee9c, Joachim Low \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eefa th\u1eb9n khi tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 Sebastian Rudy b\u1ecb v\u1ee1 m\u0169i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Tuy nhi\u00ean, nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eafc m\u1eafc t\u1ea1i sao \u00f4ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 y t\u1ebf l\u1ea1i m\u1ea5t qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1eady c\u1ee7a Sebastian Rudy.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong kho\u1ea3ng 5 ph\u00fat Sebastian Rudy v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t, \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 b\u1ecb Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u00e9p ng\u01b0\u1ee3c. Ngay sau khi Gundogan v\u00e0o s\u00e2n, h\u1ecd l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m v\u00e0 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi. May m\u1eafn h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c 2-1 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<h2>C\u00e1c tin b\u00e0i kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c 2-1 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-duc-21-thuy-dien-421-189417.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c 2-1 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/duc-nguoc-dong-kinh-di-ngay-ve-cua-marco-reus-421-189411.html\">\u0110\u1ee9c ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng kinh d\u1ecb: Ng\u00e0y v\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a Marco Reus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-joachim-low-noi-gi-ve-quyet-dinh-loai-bo-mesut-ozil-421-189410.html\">HLV Joachim Low n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf Mesut Ozil?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-thuy-dien-day-la-that-bai-cay-dang-nhat-trong-su-nghiep-cam-quan-cua-toi-421-189407.html\">HLV Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n: \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cay \u0111\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/marco-reus-noi-gi-sau-ban-thang-dau-tien-o-world-cup-421-189402.html\">Trai \u0111\u1eb9p Marco Reus n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf World Cup</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-chien-thang-dau-tim-cua-dt-duc-421-189380.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111au tim c\u1ee7a \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-joachim-loew-lai-gay-bao-khi-tai-hien-man-an-ri-mui-421-189386.html\">HLV Joachim Loew l\u1ea1i g\u00e2y b\u00e3o khi t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n m\u00e0n \u0103n ... r\u1ec9 m\u0169i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-duc-vs-thuy-dien-461-189377.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: \u0110\u1ee9c 2-1 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n (B\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"549","checkdouble":"189479"},{"date":"08:45 25/06","title":"C\u00fa hat-trick l\u1ecbch s\u1eed gi\u00fap Harry Kane t\u1ef1 tin v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/cu-hattrick-lich-su-giup-harry-kane-tu-tin-vo-dich-world-cup.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e3 52 n\u0103m ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i cho n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 sau hai chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1ef9 m\u00e3n h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u01b0\u1ee3t \u1ea3i Tunisia t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, th\u1ebf r\u1ed3i Anh \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u00f9i d\u1eadp Tunisia v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 6-1 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018. \u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Harry Kane ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi c\u00fa hat-trick \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch Vua Ph\u00e1 L\u01b0\u1edbi v\u1edbi 5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Harry Kane t\u1ef1 tin c\u00f9ng \u0110T Anh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Harry Kane t\u1ef1 tin c\u00f9ng \u0110T Anh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/Harry-Kane-tu-tin-cung-DT-Anh-vo-dich-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Harry Kane t\u1ef1 tin c\u00f9ng \u0110T Anh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng trung phong xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh s\u1ea3n sinh trong nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, Harry Kane c\u0169ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 x\u1ee9 s\u1edf s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 th\u1ee9 ba trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed l\u1eadp hat-trick \u1edf World Cup sau hai ti\u1ec1n b\u1ed1i huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Geoff Hurst (1966) v\u00e0 Gary Lineker (1986).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u00e1n c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i ngay trong k\u1ef3 World Cup \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eddi, ch\u1eb3ng ph\u1ea3i th\u1ebf m\u00e0 Harry Kane c\u00e0ng th\u00eam l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 tin s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c Totttenham sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-anh-vs-panama-463-189421.html\" target=\"_blank\">Anh 6-1 Panama</span>:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u0103ng quang ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u00e0 d\u00f9 t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u1ea3 h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh d\u00e0i tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 ni\u1ec1m tin r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0 d\u0169ng c\u1ea3m h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u00f3. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i r\u1ed3i v\u00e0 gi\u1edd s\u1ebd n\u00f3i l\u1ea1i, nh\u1eefng Premier League hay Champions League hay b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 danh hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0o c\u00f9ng Tottenham \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi World Cup.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, Anh s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n B\u1ec9 t\u1ef1a chung k\u1ebft tranh ng\u00f4i v\u1ecb s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t. C\u1ea3 hai \u00f4ng l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng t\u1eeb \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1, hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, v\u1eady n\u00ean trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a nhau th\u00ec ti\u00eau ch\u00ed fair-play l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-ly-do-giup-dt-anh-co-chien-thang-tung-bung-truoc-panama-o-world-cup-2018-421-189457.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/3-ly-do-giup-dt-anh-co-chien-thang-tung-bung-truoc-panama-o-world-cup-2018.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-ly-do-giup-dt-anh-co-chien-thang-tung-bung-truoc-panama-o-world-cup-2018-421-189457.html\">3 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap \u0110T Anh c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Panama</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Panama kh\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng kh\u00e1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1eadm 6-1. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n gi\u00fap Tam s\u01b0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"548","checkdouble":"189480"},{"date":"08:32 25/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iran vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha (01h00 ng\u00e0y 26/6): Kh\u00f3 c\u1ea3n CR7","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/iran-vs-bo-dao-nha-01h00-ngay-266-kho-can-cr7.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ronaldo \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao, v\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 b\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 thi cho h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 n\u00e0o mu\u1ed1n ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iran vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2>L\u1ea1i ph\u1ea3i nh\u00ecn CR7<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ronaldo \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec9nh cao phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 33, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 che m\u1edd t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ch\u1eb3ng sai khi cho r\u1eb1ng, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 d\u00e8 b\u1ec9u hay h\u1ea1 th\u1ea5p. B\u1edfi v\u1edbi CR7, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Fernando Santos c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha, th\u00eam 1 c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Ma R\u1ed1c, Cris Ronaldo chi\u1ebfm m\u1ecdi ti\u00eau \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0, khi s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea3 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed n\u1ebfu nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, c\u00e0ng th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 c\u1ee7a anh. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Ronaldo ghi 4 b\u00e0n sau 4 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang khung th\u00e0nh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n gi\u00e0nh k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a l\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng trong. Tuy nhi\u00ean, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Santos mu\u1ed1n k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u. V\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 ngang b\u1eb1ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha, h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi ghi c\u00e0ng nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iran vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 1\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iran vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Nhan-dinh-Iran-vs-Bo-Dao-Nha-bang-B-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec9nh cao</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t, d\u00f9 \u0111ang c\u00f9ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng, nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1eebng qu\u00ean, Ronaldo l\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00e0ng b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch, c\u00e0ng g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u \u00e1p l\u1ef1c, anh c\u00e0ng b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 d\u1eef d\u1ed9i. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y 2 \u0111\u00e0n em Romelu Lukaku c\u00f9ng Harry Kane \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1, \u201cnh\u0103m nhe\u201d danh hi\u1ec7u vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi m\u00e0 Ronaldo khao kh\u00e1t.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1edfi v\u1eady, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iran. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u00e0 th\u1eeba \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Ngo\u00e0i ra, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. \u0110\u1ec3 l\u00e0m nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o t\u1eeb to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i, thay v\u00ec qu\u00e1 ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iran vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iran vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha (01h00 ng\u00e0y 266) Kh\u00f3 c\u1ea3n CR7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/Nhan-dinh-Iran-vs-Bo-Dao-Nha-(01h00-ngay-266)-Kho-can-CR7-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u1ea7n gi\u00e0nh th\u00eam 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nIran c\u00f3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd?</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ra qu\u00e2n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng (th\u1eafng Ma R\u1ed1c 1-0), \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn T\u00e2y Ban Nha g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua b\u1eb1ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u1eabn r\u1ed9ng m\u1edf v\u1edbi \u0110T Iran t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. H\u1ecd \u0111ang x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 3, nh\u01b0ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng d\u0129 nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u1ecd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn, khi \u0111ang k\u00e9m \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u1eb7t ra, \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Iran ph\u1ea3i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1eb7t c\u00e1i \u0111\u00e3. V\u00e0 t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, vi\u1ec7c ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n Cristiano Ronaldo l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iran vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha (01h00 ng\u00e0y 266) Kh\u00f3 c\u1ea3n CR7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iran vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha (01h00 ng\u00e0y 266) Kh\u00f3 c\u1ea3n CR7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/Nhan-dinh-Iran-vs-Bo-Dao-Nha-(01h00-ngay-266)-Kho-can-CR7-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110T Iran c\u00f2n nguy\u00ean c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nTh\u1eadt may m\u1eafn, Iran \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha Carlos Queiroz \u2013 ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2008, v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a CR7. Ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, Queiroz t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0 tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd c\u1ee7a HLV huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Sir Alex Ferguson, v\u00e0 g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u00e0o s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a Ronaldo trong th\u1eddi gian \u1edf Old Trafford.</div>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n, nh\u01b0ng Iran v\u1eabn c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd ph\u00e1t huy to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. S\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn v\u00e0 b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf m\u1ecdi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng, khi Carlos Queiroz \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf ph\u1ea3n b\u1ed9i qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ti\u1ec5n B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng d\u00f9 sao, l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf v\u1eabn nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 Ronaldo c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, khi h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. \u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean, b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a CR7 t\u1ea1i World Cup (n\u0103m 2006) l\u00e0 v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi ch\u00ednh Iran, v\u00e0 anh r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. B\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n quy\u1ebft t\u1eed l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t, nh\u01b0ng li\u1ec7u ch\u1eebng \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 Iran l\u1eadp n\u00ean k\u1ef3 t\u00edch tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha?\u00a0<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iran vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" title=\"Preview Iran vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/Iran-vs-BDN.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iran vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha b\u1ea3ng B Worlde Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nTh\u00f4ng tin b\u00ean l\u1ec1</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">-B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 10/11 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i World Cup.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">-B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi 6/8 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i World Cup.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">-B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha th\u1eafng 3/4 l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u \u00c1.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">-B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Iran 2-0 trong l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i World Cup 2006.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">-Ronaldo ghi 4 b\u00e0n sau 4 c\u00fa s\u00fat tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch t\u1ea1i World Cup.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">-Iran ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>T\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Raphael Guerreiro g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1eb9 trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Ma R\u1ed1c, nh\u01b0ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cao s\u1ebd k\u1ecbp b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, HLV Carlos Queiroz s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Alireza Jahanbakhsh v\u00e0 Roozbeh Cheshmi v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iran vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha (01h00 ng\u00e0y 266) Kh\u00f3 c\u1ea3n CR7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 5\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iran vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha (01h00 ng\u00e0y 266) Kh\u00f3 c\u1ea3n CR7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 5\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/Nhan-dinh-Iran-vs-Bo-Dao-Nha-(01h00-ngay-266)-Kho-can-CR7-hinh-anh-5.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Iran vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>\u00a0</h3>\r\n<h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iran vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 6\" title=\"B\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018 sau hai l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/bang-b.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>X\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng b\u1ea3ng B World Cup sau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<h3>\u00a0</h3>\r\n<h2>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 Iran vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha: 0-1</h2>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/bang-b-world-cup-2018-kich-ban-nao-de-tay-ban-nha-va-bo-dao-nha-bi-loai-466-189140.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/bang-b-world-cup-2018-kich-ban-nao-de-tay-ban-nha-va-bo-dao-nha-bi-loai.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/bang-b-world-cup-2018-kich-ban-nao-de-tay-ban-nha-va-bo-dao-nha-bi-loai-466-189140.html\">B\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018: K\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i?</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 n\u1eafm gi\u1eef l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ho\u1eb7c T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu Iran gi\u00e0nh k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t trong lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/fan-cuong-giam-90-kg-trong-6-thang-de-duoc-gap-than-tuong-ronaldo-188-189340.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/fan-cuong-giam-90-kg-trong-6-thang-de-duoc-gap-than-tuong-ronaldo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/hau-truong/fan-cuong-giam-90-kg-trong-6-thang-de-duoc-gap-than-tuong-ronaldo-188-189340.html\">Fan cu\u1ed3ng gi\u1ea3m\u2026 90 kg trong 6 th\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eb7p th\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng Ronaldo</span><br>\r\nMarina Bogomolova ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t n\u1eef n\u1ed9i tr\u1ee3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 bao ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c cho \u0111\u1ebfn khi c\u00f4 t\u1ef1 quay m\u1ed9t \u0111o\u1ea1n video v\u1ec1 h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n, h\u1ecdc ti\u1ebfng Anh,...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ly-do-hai-huoc-khien-ronaldo-quyet-dinh-nuoi-rau-de-421-189143.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/cristiano-ronaldo-cropped_1f5krpdeo1lzf11ohj93twdos5.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ly-do-hai-huoc-khien-ronaldo-quyet-dinh-nuoi-rau-de-421-189143.html\">L\u00fd do h\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc khi\u1ebfn Ronaldo quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh nu\u00f4i r\u00e2u d\u00ea</span><br>\r\nSau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Ma R\u1ed1c v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u, si\u00eau sao Cristiano Ronaldo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 r\u00e2u r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"547","checkdouble":"189482"},{"date":"08:43 25/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Nga (21h ng\u00e0y 25/7): H\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/nhan-dinh-uruguay-vs-nga-21h-ngay-257-hai-long-voi-chinh-minh.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Nga \u2013 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e2n tranh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng A World Cup 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1ch bung s\u1ee9c l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi nhau b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>B\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea3 Nga v\u00e0 Uruguay \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean d\u00f9 c\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ed1ng nhau. Nga b\u1ecf l\u1ea1i ph\u00eda sau chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng b\u1ebft b\u00e1t \u1edf ph\u00eda sau \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. \u1ede 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 qua, \u201cNh\u1eefng ch\u00fa g\u1ea5u\u201d l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u00f9i d\u1eadp Saudi Arabia 5-0 v\u00e0 Ai C\u1eadp 3-1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, Uruguay \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n v\u1edbi c\u1eb7p song s\u00e1t Luis Suarez v\u00e0 Edinson Cavani l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c. \u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, h\u1ecd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Ai C\u1eadp 1-0 nh\u1edd b\u00e0n th\u1eafng mu\u1ed9n c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Jose Gimenez. K\u1ebf \u0111\u1ebfn, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u Saudi Arabia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Nga (21h ng\u00e0y 257) H\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Nga (21h ng\u00e0y 257) H\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/Nhan-dinh-Uruguay-vs-Nga-(21h-ngay-257)-Hai-long-voi-chinh-minh-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Uruguay ch\u01b0a thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng nh\u01b0 mong \u0111\u1ee3i</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00ean l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft, nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Nga s\u1ebd l\u00e0 v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e2n tranh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng A World Cup 2018. T\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Samara Arena, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga mu\u1ed1n cho th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 tham v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9, kh\u00f4ng tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 x\u1ee9 b\u1ea1ch d\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00e0o mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n thi\u1ebfu \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f2n Uruguay, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn. Sau 2 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 1-0, c\u00e1c C\u0110V ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a La Celeste s\u1ebd gi\u00e0u c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng h\u01a1n, ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng h\u01a1n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i \u201cs\u00e1t th\u1ee7\u201d Suarez v\u00e0 Cavani.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>T\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ra qu\u00e2n v\u1edbi Ai C\u1eadp, Suarez \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a Uruguay. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf, phong th\u00e1i n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1, ch\u1eadm ch\u1ea1p c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Barcelona c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 lo l\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Suarez mo ty so cho Uruguay\" title=\"Suarez m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho Uruguay\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/chuc-mung-luis-suarez-cuu-sao-mu-tien-the-he-lo-loi-moi-gia-nhap-barca.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Suarez \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i c\u01a1n kh\u00e1t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Suarez suy gi\u1ea3m t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean khi anh \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc qua tu\u1ed5i 31. Nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 th\u00ednh nh\u1ea1y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a El Pistolero n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t nguy hi\u1ec3m cho Uruguay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eadt may l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebfn m\u1ea5t trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc Saudi Arabia, b\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Suarez \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Uruguay c\u00f3 tr\u1ecdn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edbm gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out World Cup 2018. \u1ede \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e1ch s\u1ed1 9 ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed, tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Uruguay vs Nga\" title=\"Preview Uruguay vs Nga\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-2562018.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Nga 21h ng\u00e0y 25/6</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n Suarez tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c giao cho b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i: Trung v\u1ec7 Sergey Ignashevich v\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i Yuri Zhirkov c\u1ee7a Nga. Ch\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Uruguay s\u1ebd ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu xung quanh khu v\u1ef1c m\u00e0 hai l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng s\u1eafp 39 v\u00e0 35 tu\u1ed5i tr\u1ea5n gi\u1eef. \u0110\u1ec3 Nga c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a nh\u1eb1m gi\u1eef v\u1eefng ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng A, vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a Ignashevich v\u00e0 Zhirkov l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid, Jose Gimenez v\u00e0 Diego Godin b\u00ean ph\u00eda Uruguay c\u0169ng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng. D\u00f9 l\u00e0 Fedor Semedov hay Artem Dzyuba \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i r\u1ea5t c\u1ea3nh gi\u00e1c. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a hai m\u0169i c\u00f4ng Nga l\u00e0 ng\u00f3n \u0111\u00f2n s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd trong 2 tr\u1eadn qua.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Nga k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi l\u0103ng k\u00ednh c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi ngo\u00e0i cu\u1ed9c. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ch\u00fang ta cho r\u1eb1ng l\u00e0 logic v\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng A. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Uruguay v\u00e0 Nga c\u00f3 t\u00ednh to\u00e1n g\u00ec, ch\u1ec9 h\u1ecd m\u1edbi bi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Oi nuoc Nga yeu dau cua toi!\" title=\"\u00d4i n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga y\u00eau d\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i!\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/bai-du-thi-an-tuong-world-cup-2018-gau-nga-khong-con-ngu-dong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">M\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ee7 gi\u00fap Nga c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi m\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi l\u00e0 hai \u00f4ng l\u1edbn ch\u00e2u \u00c2u: T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, th\u1ef1c ra c\u00e1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0 m\u1ea5t v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng hay nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Uruguay v\u00e0 Nga kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng. Bung s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi nhau v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n nguy c\u01a1 \u201cqu\u00e8 qu\u1eb7t\u201d nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n t\u1edbi v\u1edbi c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1ebd b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nK\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi Uruguay v\u00e0 Nga th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 mu\u1ed1n th\u1eafng, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 v\u1ed3 v\u1eadp. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1ebd tr\u1ecdn phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ea7m ch\u1eebng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u01a1 h\u1edf v\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:<br>\r\nUruguay (4-4-2): </strong>1.Muslera - 4.Varela, 2.Gim\u00e9nez, 3.God\u00edn, 22.C\u00e1ceres - 5.S\u00e1nchez, 6.Bentancur, 15.Vecino, 7.Rodr\u00edguez - 9.Su\u00e1rez, 21.Cavani<br>\r\n<strong>Nga (4-2-3-1): </strong>1.Akinfeev - 2.Fernandes, 3.Kutepov, 4.Ignashevich, 18.Zhirkov - 11.Zobnin, 8.Gazinskiy - 19.Samedov, 17.Golovin, 6.Cheryshev - 10.Smolov<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: H\u00f2a 0-0<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Uruguay vs Nga\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Uruguay vs Nga\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/DH-Uruguay-vs-Nga-(4-4-2-vs-4-2-3-1).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Uruguay vs Nga</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T Nga tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/co-doi-bong-chi-25-trieu-bang-mua-trai-dep-tuyen-nga-421-189263.html\">C\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng chi 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua trai \u0111\u1eb9p tuy\u1ec3n Nga</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nguoi-hung-dt-nga-muon-cham-tran-doi-thu-nao-o-vong-knockout-421-189236.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng \u0110T Nga mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o \u1edf v\u00f2ng knock-out?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-yeu-to-giup-nga-da-bai-ai-cap-tai-world-cup-2018-421-189081.html\">3 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 gi\u00fap Nga \u0111\u1ea3 b\u1ea1i Ai C\u1eadp t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-nga-31-ai-cap-421-189075.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Nga 3-1 Ai C\u1eadp</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"546","checkdouble":"189485"},{"date":"08:43 25/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh TBN vs Mar\u1ed1c (1h ng\u00e0y 26/6): \u0110\u1ebfn l\u00fac La Roja b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/25/nhan-dinh-tbn-vs-maroc-1h-ngay-266-den-luc-la-roja-bung-no.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 \u00fd. Tuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh TBN vs Mar\u1ed1c v\u1eabn tin v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng d\u00e0nh cho \u201cB\u00f2 t\u00f3t\u201d.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>TBN m\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i kh\u00e1t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau khi b\u1ecb B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a b\u1edfi c\u00fa s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo, T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. H\u1ecd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Iran 1-0 \u1edf m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 b\u1ea3ng B tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Kazan Arena.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Iran \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mar\u1ed1c v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ea7y quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m, T\u00e2y Ban Nha g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. H\u1ecd tr\u1ea3i qua qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ea7y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u1edfi Iran \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5 b\u00ea t\u00f4ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, kh\u00e9p ch\u1eb7t h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng m\u00e0 TBN c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh TBN vs Mar\u1ed1c (1h ng\u00e0y 266) \u0110\u1ebfn l\u00fac La Roja b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh TBN vs Mar\u1ed1c (1h ng\u00e0y 266) \u0110\u1ebfn l\u00fac La Roja b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/Nhan-dinh-TBN-vs-Maroc-(1h-ngay-266)-Den-luc-La-Roja-bung-no-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">T\u00e2y Ban Nha nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Iran 1-0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edbi ph\u00fat 54, T\u00e2y Ban Nha m\u1edbi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t sau khi Diego Costa t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t pha b\u00f3ng l\u00f3ng ng\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Iran. Qua \u0111\u00f3, d\u00f9 nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n song La Roja v\u1eabn c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha t\u1ea1m n\u1eafm 2 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u1edbi c\u00f9ng 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh TBN vs Mar\u1ed1c gi\u1edd s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u1eabu sao, \u1edf chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iran, T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1eabn b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u00e1ng m\u1eebng. \u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 \u1edf h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i. S\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Dani Carvajal sau khi b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap La Roja c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng h\u01a1n khi so v\u1edbi c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i c\u1ee7a Jordi Alba.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-tbn-vs-iran-ton-vinh-bong-da-phong-ngu-421-189122.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/Iran-qua-cam-truoc-TBN-Doi-khi-bong-da-phong-ngu-cung-can-duoc-ton-vinh-hinh-anh-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-tbn-vs-iran-ton-vinh-bong-da-phong-ngu-421-189122.html\">Iran qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc TBN: \u0110\u00f4i khi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00f4n vinh</span><br>\r\n<span>D\u01b0 \u00e2m TBN vs Iran b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd n\u00ean m\u1ea1nh d\u1ea1n t\u00f4n vinh chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 tr\u00ean h\u1ebft, tinh th\u1ea7n ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n T\u00e2y \u00c1 khi...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCarvajal c\u00f9ng Lucas Vazquez t\u1ea1o n\u00ean nh\u1eefng n\u00e9t \u0111\u1eb7c s\u1eafc h\u01a1n cho T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Thay v\u00ec nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n qua l\u1ea1i, 2 c\u00e1i t\u00ean tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f2 m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng hai bi\u00ean h\u01a1n. Nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1t t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd gi\u00fap TBN c\u00f3 th\u00eam ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u1eefu hi\u1ec7u tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Iran. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 qu\u00ean ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Diego Costa. 4 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn ph\u1ea3i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t t\u1ea1i World Cup 2014. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi sinh t\u1ea1i Brazil b\u1ecb cho l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi phong c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a La Roja v\u00e0 c\u00e1 t\u00ednh m\u1ea1nh, \u0111\u00f4i l\u00fac hung h\u00e3n c\u1ee7a anh c\u0169ng b\u1ecb ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"TBN vs Iran Costa an mung\" title=\"TBN vs Iran Costa an mung\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/du-am-iran-01-tbn-ngay-quai-thu-khuat-phuc-chien-binh-ba-tu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Costa ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y, Costa \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng nghi ng\u1edd d\u00e0nh cho m\u00ecnh bi\u1ebfn m\u1ea5t. 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n l\u00e0 minh ch\u1ee9ng r\u00f5 n\u00e9t. V\u00e0 khi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iran, l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 anh gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u1edfi b\u1ecf nh\u1eefng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u00fac ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft c\u1ee5c thi\u1ebfu bi quan. Tuy nhi\u00ean, d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 Costa \u1edf tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng do HLV Fernando Hierro d\u1eabn d\u1eaft lu\u00f4n tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y.</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn l\u00fac La Roja b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh hai \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp l\u00e0 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00e0 Iran \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9, T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t Mar\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i. 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 qua, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u Phi ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3i ch\u00fat n\u00e0o. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iran v\u00e0 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, h\u1ecd t\u1eeb nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n t\u1edbi \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o v\u1ec1 th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Tay Ban Nha vs Maroc\" title=\"Preview T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs Mar\u1ed1c\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/Tay-Ban-Nha-vs-Maroc.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh TBN vs Mar\u1ed1c 1h ng\u00e0y 26/6</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00f3, Mar\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra kh\u00f4ng \u00edt nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. T\u00ednh ra, t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m 2 tr\u1eadn g\u1ed9p l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Hakim Ziyech c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00ean t\u1edbi 28 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o. Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh t\u1edbi t\u1eeb kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng k\u1ebft th\u00fac y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m c\u1ee7a Mar\u1ed1c. T\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng h\u1ecd c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i Mar\u1ed1c l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc T\u00e2y Ban Nha. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u Phi \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i sau 2 tr\u1eadn tr\u1eafng tay v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kh\u00e1t \u0111i\u1ec3m. Ch\u1ec9 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00f3 v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out World Cup 2018 nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bo dao nha maroc\" title=\"B\u1ed3 \u0111\u00e0o nha mar\u1ed1c\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/1529501040692_lc_galleryImage_Morocco_s_defender_Mehdi_.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mar\u1ed1c b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 s\u1ef1 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf sau 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh TBN vs Mar\u1ed1c tin l\u00e0 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. M\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, n\u1ebfu l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o cho T\u00e2y Ban Nha. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u1edf ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea1p v\u1ec1 tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 La Roja b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ti\u1ebfp theo nhi\u1ec1u ch\u00f4ng gai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Mar\u1ed1c c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn T\u00e2y Ban Nha qu\u00e1 e ng\u1ea1i. M\u1ed9t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00f4i c\u00f4ng tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i d\u00e0nh cho h\u1ecd s\u1ebd thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi khi \u0111\u00e1 v\u1edbi Iran t\u1eed th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ebfm \u0111i\u1ec3m. V\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e2n Kaliningrad s\u1ebd ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 t\u1eeb Costa c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:<br>\r\nTBN (4-3-3): </strong>1.De Gea - 2.Carvajal, 3.Piqu\u00e9, 15.Ramos, 18.Alba - 10.Thiago, 5.Busquets, 6.Iniesta - 22.Isco, 19.Costa, 21.Silva<br>\r\n<strong>Mar\u1ed1c (4-2-3-1):</strong> 12.Munir - 17.Dirar, 5.Benatia, 4.Costa, 2.Hakimi - 14.Boussoufa, 8.Ahmadi - 16.Amrabat, 10.Belhanda, 7.Ziyech - 9.Kaabi<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: TBN th\u1eafng 3-0<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Tay Ban Nha vs Maroc\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs Mar\u1ed1c\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/Tay-Ban-Nha-vs-Maroc-(4-3-3-vs-4-2-3-1).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs Mar\u1ed1c</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-iran-01-tbn-ngay-quai-thu-khuat-phuc-chien-binh-ba-tu-421-189121.html\">Iran 0-1 TBN: Ng\u00e0y &ldquo;Qu\u00e1i th\u00fa&rdquo; khu\u1ea5t ph\u1ee5c &ldquo;Chi\u1ebfn binh Ba T\u01b0&rdquo;</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-dieu-rut-ra-sau-du-am-iran-vs-tay-ban-nha-421-189116.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n 1-0 c\u1ee7a TBN tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iran</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/iniesta-thua-nhan-tbn-anh-huong-tam-ly-boi-be-boi-lopetegui-421-189085.html\">Iniesta th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn TBN \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u00e2m l\u00fd b\u1edfi b\u00ea b\u1ed1i Lopetegui</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-hierro-khong-muon-dt-tay-ban-nha-di-vao-vet-xe-do-cua-nguoi-duc-421-188972.html\">HLV Hierro kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111i v\u00e0o v\u1ebft xe \u0111\u1ed5 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"545","checkdouble":"189488"}]}